{"tid":2294841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泰國「壞學生」抗議組織歡樂上街頭","createTime":"2020-11-21T10:12:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T11:01:55.000Z","uid":337052,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5f6f5dd5d740812a5b2b2453ca004076935f9d2f","tid":2294841,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T10:12:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">受降雨影響 &ldquo;壞學生&ldquo;組織轉至Siam站附近集會</span></strong><br />\n2020年11月21日 - by hushjoker<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thaiheadlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE_20201121151643-735x400.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thaiheadlines.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259B%25BE_20201121151643-735x400.png&h=e9174025&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n泰國頭條新聞社訊據泰媒報導名為&ldquo;壞學生&rdquo;的集會組織此前宣布將於11月21日13時在Ratchaprasong岔路口舉行集會，但由於今日曼谷降雨影響，13時12分，集會組織發文表示將集會地點轉移至Siam BTS站台下方。<br />\n <br />\n15時，集會人員已陸續下至拉瑪一路，巴吞灣警署已關閉拉瑪一路巴吞灣岔道口至Chaloem Phao 岔道口路段，集會組織頭領開始設置舞台準備演講。 （編譯：hush 來源：Thairath、Khaosod、JS100）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thaiheadlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/EnVS-b0WEAMqV1_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thaiheadlines.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2FEnVS-b0WEAMqV1_.jpg&h=38eff767&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thaiheadlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/EnVS-GBW4AE_n6z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thaiheadlines.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2FEnVS-GBW4AE_n6z.jpg&h=b171fc40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thaiheadlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/EnVTV9pXIAMhiPk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thaiheadlines.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2FEnVTV9pXIAMhiPk.jpg&h=ef2c3c48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thaiheadlines.com/%e5%8f%97%e9%99%8d%e9%9b%a8%e5%bd%b1%e5%93%8d-%e5%9d%8f%e5%ad%a6%e7%94%9f%e7%bb%84%e7%bb%87%e8%bd%ac%e8%87%b3siam%e7%ab%99%e9%99%84%e8%bf%91%e9%9b%86%e4%bc%9a/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thaiheadlines.com%2F%25e5%258f%2597%25e9%2599%258d%25e9%259b%25a8%25e5%25bd%25b1%25e5%2593%258d-%25e5%259d%258f%25e5%25ad%25a6%25e7%2594%259f%25e7%25bb%2584%25e7%25bb%2587%25e8%25bd%25ac%25e8%2587%25b3siam%25e7%25ab%2599%25e9%2599%2584%25e8%25bf%2591%25e9%259b%2586%25e4%25bc%259a%2F&d=HaoFMq3H8OfxnxI562yM31Ln0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=edb46458\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thaiheadlines.com/%e5%8f%97%e9%99%8d%e9%9b%a8%e5%bd%b1%e5%93%8d-%e5%9d%8f%e5%ad%a6%e7%94%9f%e7%bb%84%e7%bb%87%e8%bd%ac%e8%87%b3siam%e7%ab%99%e9%99%84%e8%bf%91%e9%9b%86%e4%bc%9a/</a>"},{"pid":"923c4d45718e0e9d10c65f3a429aec812052943b","tid":2294841,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T10:13:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jN5KTgY8ZqM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjN5KTgY8ZqM&d=HaoFMq3H8OfxnxI562yM31Ln0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=7b52ef96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jN5KTgY8ZqM</a>"},{"pid":"1f4f28086bfba3bd9ee46c0fb64b1fddfb185a04","tid":2294841,"uid":79117,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T10:14:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ed9e00e03306ae1b4fdaa8118fa8e6992e9d12d","tid":2294841,"uid":54721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T10:14:13.000Z","msg":"快樂抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f405c1adfaffef592f43665eeb074699f10e69d6","tid":2294841,"uid":48631,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T10:14:50.000Z","msg":"叫埋lunch哥啦"},{"pid":"b3cf67a82ecda660607ae84a523939c805e87d4b","tid":2294841,"uid":21716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"923c4d45718e0e9d10c65f3a429aec812052943b","tid":2294841,"uid":337052,